Dataset Attribution
-------------------

This crate's companion paper evaluates the DSFB observer on ten public
robotics and prognostics datasets. Each dataset retains its own upstream
licence. The dsfb-robotics crate redistributes only stratified slices (or,
where upstream terms require, manifest-only pointers with SHA-256 checksums)
under the original dataset licences. Full datasets must be obtained by the
user from the original providers under those providers' terms. See
`data/slices/SLICE_MANIFEST.json` and the per-dataset oracle-protocol
documents under `docs/` for provenance, licence, and fetch instructions.
